---
description : Découvrez le portfolio de Charles Cantin, un photographe professionnel basé à Paris. Explorez une collection variée de travaux de photographie artistique, de portraits intemporels, de paysages à couper le souffle et de moments de mariage inoubliables. Inspirez-vous de la passion et de la créativité capturées dans chaque image.
layout : layout.njk
title : Portfolio
styles:
        - /assets/css/portfolio.css
script : "portfolio.js" 
---

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="photoh2 row text-center hideleft">
      <h1>PORTFOLIO</h1>
      <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
        <ul class="breadcrumb justify-content-center">
          <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="{{'/accueil/' | url}}">Accueil</a></li>
          <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">Gallerie</li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container mt-5 pb-5 d-flex justify-content-center">
    <div class="container-btn row row-cols-3 row-cols-md-1 justify-content-center pb-5 w-75 hideright">
      <!-- filter buttons -->
      <button 
      type="button" 
      class="btn btn-primary-outline filter-btn me-sm-3 me-md-4 w-auto " 
      data-id="all">
      All
      </button>
      {%- set categories = [] -%}
      {%- for post in collections.post -%}
        {%- if post.data.category not in categories -%}
          {%- set categories = categories.concat(post.data.category) -%}
          <button 
          type="button" 
          class="btn btn-primary-outline filter-btn me-sm-3 me-md-4 w-auto" 
          data-id="{{ post.data.category }}">
          {{ post.data.category }}
          </button>
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- container ITEMS -->
  <div class="container mt-5 pb-5">
    <div class="row maincontent row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 row-cols-lg-3 g-4 mx-5 pt5">
            
{%- for post in collections.post -%}
  <div 
    class="col-photo col d-flex justify-content-center hideright" 
      data-category="{{ post.data.category }}">
    <div class="card border border-0 shadow h-25 w-75">
      <img 
      src="{{ post.data.image }}" 
      class="card-img" 
      alt="{{ post.data.imageAlt }}" 
      loading="lazy">
    </div>
  </div>
{%- endfor -%}

{# ENLARGED onclick image #}
  <div class="enlarge">
    <span> &times; </span>
    <img src="" alt="">
  </div>

    </div>
  </div>
